<jaN0001>Shuhei
<enN0001>Shuhei

///================================================================================

//TEXT
<jaT0001>While I was calculating the enemy's intentions, he came within several meters from us.
<enT0001>While I was calculating the enemy's intentions, he came within several meters from us.

//TEXT
<jaT0002>Then he paused and watched us.
<enT0002>Then he paused and watched us.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0003>"(Now what are you going to do?)"
<enT0003>"(Now what are you going to do?)"

//TEXT
<jaT0004>Because of that shield, I can't attack until he's a little closer. All we can do is watch for now.
<enT0004>Because of that shield, I can't attack until he's a little closer. All we can do is watch for now.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0005>"(Hmm? He's stirring around?)"
<enT0005>"(Hmm? He's stirring around?)"

//TEXT
<jaT0006>The man placed his hand inside his chest, readying something. Is he readying something to attack us with?
<enT0006>The man placed his hand inside his chest, readying something. Is he readying something to attack us with?

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0007>"......"
<enT0007>"......"

//TEXT
<jaT0008>I had a bad feeling about this. What should I do? I can't wait for him to get any closer, and I can't let him finish readying whatever it is he's preparing.
<enT0008>I had a bad feeling about this. What should I do? I can't wait for him to get any closer, and I can't let him finish readying whatever it is he's preparing.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0009>"(What to do? Should I close the shutter? Or should I go in?)"
<enT0009>"(What to do? Should I close the shutter? Or should I go in?)"

//TEXT
<jaT0010>While I pondered, the man threw something black from behind the shield. The next instant, he fell back at full speed behind the shield.
<enT0010>While I pondered, the man threw something black from behind the shield. The next instant, he fell back at full speed behind the shield.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0011>"Oh shit!! Everyone get back!"
<enT0011>"Oh shit!! Everyone get back!"

//TEXT
<jaT0012>Finally, I realized his intentions. I ordered everyone to get away and leapt towards that black thing he threw, but it was already too late.
<enT0012>Finally, I realized his intentions. I ordered everyone to get away and leapt towards that black thing he threw, but it was already too late.

//TEXT
<jaT0013>A tremendous explosion. The next instant, my entire body was swallowed in a storm of light.
<enT0013>A tremendous explosion. The next instant, my entire body was swallowed in a storm of light.

//TEXT
<jaT0014>......
<enT0014>......

